        <div rend="parallel">
          <p xml:id="Kali117-kilavi">iḵtu āṟṟiṭait talaivaṉ talaiviyaik kaiyatu viṉāyc cērntatu.</p>
          <p xml:lang="en"></p>
        </div>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="Kali117">
                <l>māṇa vurukkiya naṉpoṉ maṇiyuṟīip </l>
                <l>pēṇit tuṭaittaṉṉa mēṉiyāy kōṅkiṉ </l>
                <l>mutirā viḷamukai yoppa vetiriya </l>
                <l>toyyil poṟitta vaṉamulaiyāy maṟṟuniṉ </l>
                <l>kaiya tevaṉmaṟ ṟurai; </l>
                <l rend="space">kaiyatai, cērik kiḻavaṉ makaḷēṉyāṉ maṟṟiḵtōr </l>
                <l>mātarp pulaitti vilaiyākac ceytatōr </l>
                <l>pōḻiṟ puṉainta varippuṭṭil puṭṭilu ḷeṉṉuḷa </l>
                <l>kāṇṭakkā yeṟkāṭṭik kāṇ;</l>
                <l rend="space">kāṇiṉi, tōṭṭār katuppiṉeṉ ṟōḻi yavaroṭu </l>
                <l>kāṭṭuccārk koyta ciṟumullai maṟṟivai </l>
                <l>mullai yivaiyāyiṉ muṟṟiya kūḻaiyā </l>
                <l>yellīṟṟup pōḻtāyi ṉītōḷik kaṇṭēṉāṟ </l>
                <l>celleṉṟu niṉṉai viṭuveṉyāṉ maṟṟeṉakku </l>
                <l>melliya tōrā vaṟivu.</l>
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
                <l>You with a body that is like sapphire inlaid in good gold </l>
                <l corresp="1-2c">that was gloriously molten, cherished [and] polished,</l>
                <l corresp="4">you with beautiful breasts smeared with sandal paste</l>
                <l corresp="2d-3">that faces on equal terms the immature young buds of the Caung tree,</l>
                <l corresp="5">what is the thing in your hand? Tell [me].</l>
                <l>About what is in my hand – I am the daughter of the quarter’s chief.</l>
                <l>This is a lines basked fashioned out of leather straps</l>
                <l>that was made for sale by a beautiful washer woman. – What is in the basket?</l>
                <l corresp="6-9">You who are fit to be seen, show  me, look.</l>
                <l>Look now, these are little jasmine [buds] I plucked in the wilderness</l>
                <l>with my friends for our hair full of petals.</l>
                <l>If these are jasmine [buds], you with perfect hair,</l>
                <l>if it is a time that has light, these are rows(?) I have seen indeed.</l>
                <l>I will say “go” [and] let you go. To me</l>
                <l corresp="10-15">it is something soft, the knowledge that is not regarded.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
